{"tid":416541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(PS4) FIFA18 ProClub 新球會招收 有經驗球員","createTime":"2017-09-28T00:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T00:36:41.000Z","uid":103749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a237fc5e2b887ec517fb3b5f49dfbc1b908694ca","tid":416541,"uid":103749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T00:24:47.000Z","msg":"本球會現正招收 有潛質及有位置感之球員。<br />\n<br />\n本球會以4-2-3-1/ 4-3-3 為基本隊型<br />\n平日大約晚上9:00～1:00上線 如人數許可可以再夜少少。(假日看球員人數決定)<br />\n<br />\n球會宗旨：以整體利益（Tika Taka）為出發點,不個人主義，與其他隊友有良好溝通，配合領隊指示發輝出各隊員應有實力。<br />\n<br />\n球隊日後將會參加本地比賽以增加經驗及改善踢法為目標。<br />\n<br />\n以下是招收球員位置<br />\n<br />\n前峰一名：主要可以做到hold波 等其他隊友上前交波及有一定門前把握力。<br />\n<br />\n翼峰一名：主要可以拉空對方球員有一定扭球技術，如果前方太多人可以傳波比中場再次組織。<br />\n<br />\n兩閘各一名：有良好防守意識，不會亂出腳，壓迫對手橫傳機會。有必要時可同翼峰overlap 。<br />\n<br />\n中堅2名：有良好防守意識可配合中場組織。最好有一定控球能力不會亂解圍。<br />\n<br />\n龍門一名：有快速的反應能力，看準時機出迎，可同後防溝通配合組織。<br />\n<br />\n有意者可TG:<a href=\"http://t.me/JunoCheng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FJunoCheng&d=QGukf3mHzGPphSMpe6Xcxf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=8b8ff70c\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/JunoCheng</a> / <a href=\"https://t.me/Easy2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FEasy2s&d=QGukf3mHzGPphSMpe6Xcxf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=79b6d957\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Easy2s</a>"},{"pid":"3d76613facc6569abe51c6e785cf3d1cddbed968","tid":416541,"uid":103749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T00:36:41.000Z","msg":"有意者可TG:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/JunoCheng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FJunoCheng&d=QGukf3mHzGPphSMpe6Xcxf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=8b8ff70c\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/JunoCheng</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Easy2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FEasy2s&d=QGukf3mHzGPphSMpe6Xcxf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=79b6d957\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Easy2s</a>"}]}